  "title": "Edmonton Squash Club To Implement the COVID-19 Restriction Exemption Program",
  "excerpt": "Update September 19th: In order to have your FOB activated from September 20th onwards, the ESC is requiring proof-of-vaccination. The current easiest method of getting this documentation is by entering your PHC#, DOB and Date of your vaccination online here: https://albertavaccinerecord.ca/ You can upload the PDF generated from this website with your proof-of-vaccination via the &#8230; Read more",
  "content": "\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Update September 19th:</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">In order to have your FOB activated from September 20th onwards, the ESC is requiring proof-of-vaccination.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The current easiest method of getting this documentation is by entering your PHC#, DOB and Date of your vaccination online here: <a href=\"https://albertavaccinerecord.ca/\">https://albertavaccinerecord.ca/</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">You can upload the PDF generated from this website with your proof-of-vaccination via the secure file upload form below</p>\n\n\n\n                <div class='gf_browser_unknown gform_wrapper gravity-theme gform-theme--no-framework' data-form-theme='gravity-theme' data-form-index='0' id='gform_wrapper_90' >\n                        <div class='gform_heading'>\n                            <h2 class=\"gform_title\">COVID-19 Proof of Vaccination Upload</h2>\n                            <p class='gform_description'>File Upload for Proof of Vaccination</p>\n                        </div><form method='post' enctype='multipart/form-data'  id='gform_90'  action='/wp-json/wp/v2/posts?per_page=100&#038;page=1&#038;status=publish' data-formid='90' novalidate>\n                        <div class='gform-body gform_body'><div id='gform_fields_90' class='gform_fields top_label form_sublabel_below description_below validation_below'><div id=\"field_90_3\" class=\"gfield gfield--type-honeypot gform_validation_container field_sublabel_below gfield--has-description field_description_below field_validation_below gfield_visibility_visible\"  ><label class='gfield_label gform-field-label' for='input_90_3'>Company</label><div class='ginput_container'><input name='input_3' id='input_90_3' type='text' value='' autocomplete='new-password'/></div><div class='gfield_description' id='gfield_description_90_3'>This field is for validation purposes and should be left unchanged.</div></div